       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    ARI80202.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA ARI80202.
      *
      *     Utilizadores
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE ARI80202         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE ARCD0103 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE ARCD2000 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE ARCD2200 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIACW001 END-EXEC
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY ARCV8020.
       COPY ARCV8021.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY ARCK0001.
       COPY ARCK0002.
       COPY VIAL0015.
      *
       COPY ARCL2505.
       COPY ETCL0002.
       COPY VIATK001.
       COPY ARCL2205.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            VARIAVEIS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 AUX-CPERFIL                  PIC X(12).
           05 WS-PROGNAME                  PIC X(08) VALUE 'ARI80202'.
           05 WS-APLIC-LENGTH              PIC 9(02) VALUE ZEROES.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-ARVT0100                 PIC X(08) VALUE 'ARVT0100'.
           05 CON-ARVT2000                 PIC X(08) VALUE 'ARVT2000'.
           05 CON-ARVT2200                 PIC X(08) VALUE 'ARVT2200'.
           05 CON-CPARAM                   PIC X(10) VALUE 'GEMPRESA'.
           05 CON-CAPLIC                   PIC X(02) VALUE 'AR'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE ARI80202         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *
       COPY VIAL0004.
      *
            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.
      *
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
                 THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
      *
       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.
      *
           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO ARCV8020-MSG.
           MOVE ARCV8020-ASE               TO ARCV8021-ASE.
           MOVE ARCV8020-ADE               TO ARCV8021-ADE.
      *
           IF NOT VIAL0001-CRIACAO
      * Obtem master do perfil do utilizador logado
              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 PERFORM 1200-OBT-MASTER-USER
                    THRU 1200-OBT-MASTER-USER-EXIT
              END-IF

      * Obtem master do user introduzido de input
              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 PERFORM 1300-OBT-MASTER-PERFIL
                    THRU 1300-OBT-MASTER-PERFIL-EXIT
              END-IF

      *Valida se ambos os perfis tęm o mesmo master
      *Compara se aux-perfil (master do user logado) é igual
      *ao ARCL2505-CPERFILMAST que é o master do perfil de input

              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 IF AUX-CPERFIL NOT EQUAL TO ARCL2505-CPERFILMAST
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO ARCV8021-CPERFIL-S
                    MOVE ARCK0001-PERFIL-INVA
                      TO ARCV8021-CPERFIL-MSG
                    MOVE ARCK0002-CAPLIC-AR
                      TO ARCV8021-CPERFIL-CAPLIC
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   1200-OBT-MASTER-USER
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1200-OBT-MASTER-USER.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1200-OBT-MASTER-USER'  TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'VIAL0001-CUTILIZA-I '  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  VIAL0001-CUTILIZA-I    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE ARCL2505-COMMAREA REPLACING NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                             ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES.

           SET ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS TO TRUE.


           MOVE VIAL0001-CUTILIZA-I        TO ARCL2505-CUSERID.

           CALL ARCL2505-ROTINA USING ETCL0002-COMMAREA
                                      ARCL2505-COMMAREA.
           IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
              MOVE ARCL2505-CPERFILMAST TO AUX-CPERFIL
           ELSE
              MOVE ETCL0002-IND-ERROS
                TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                TO ARCV8021-CPERFIL-S
              MOVE ETCL0002-NR-ERRO
                TO ARCV8021-CPERFIL-MSG
              MOVE ARCK0002-CAPLIC-AR
                TO ARCV8021-CPERFIL-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

       1200-OBT-MASTER-USER-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   1300-OBT-MASTER-PERFIL.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1300-OBT-MASTER-PERFIL.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1300-OBT-MASTER-PERFIL-USER' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE ARCL2505-COMMAREA REPLACING NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                             ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES.

           MOVE ARCV8020-GUSERNAME         TO ARCL2505-CUSERID.

           CALL ARCL2505-ROTINA USING ETCL0002-COMMAREA
                                      ARCL2505-COMMAREA.

           IF NOT ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
              MOVE ETCL0002-IND-ERROS
                TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                TO ARCV8021-CPERFIL-S
              MOVE ETCL0002-ST-ERRO
                TO ARCV8021-CPERFIL-MSG
              MOVE ARCK0002-CAPLIC-AR
                TO ARCV8021-CPERFIL-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

       1300-OBT-MASTER-PERFIL-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.

           MOVE VIAL0001-IDIOMA            TO ARCV8020-CLINGUA
                                              ARCV8021-CLINGUA

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                PERFORM 2050-OBTEM-EMPRESA
                   THRU 2059-OBTEM-EMPRESA-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                PERFORM 2100-OBTEM-DADOS
                   THRU 2199-OBTEM-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND VIAL0001-CRIACAO
                PERFORM 2200-CALC-OTP
                   THRU 2200-CALC-OTP-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND VIAL0001-MODIFICACAO
              IF ARCV8020-GUSERNAME EQUAL VIAL0001-CUTILIZA-I
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                                           TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                                           TO ARCV8021-GUSERNAME-S
                 MOVE ARCK0001-N-ALTERA-USER-UPD
                                           TO ARCV8021-GUSERNAME-MSG
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      ******************************************************************
      *                  2050-OBTEM-EMPRESA                            *
      ******************************************************************
       2050-OBTEM-EMPRESA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2050-OBTEM-EMPRESA  '  TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           INITIALIZE ARCL2205-DATA

           MOVE CON-CPARAM                 TO ARCL2205-CPARAM
           MOVE CON-CAPLIC                 TO ARCL2205-CAPLIC

           PERFORM CALL-ARM2206
              THRU CALL-ARM2206-EXIT.

           IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
              MOVE ARCL2205-GVALOR1        TO ARCV8020-CEMPRESA
                                              ARCV8021-CEMPRESA
           ELSE
              SET ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS       TO TRUE
              MOVE ALL 'X'                 TO ARCV8020-CEMPRESA
                                              ARCV8021-CEMPRESA
           END-IF.

       2059-OBTEM-EMPRESA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2100-OBTEM-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2100-OBTEM-DADOS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-OBTEM-DADOS        ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'ARCV8020-GUSERNAME      ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  ARCV8020-GUSERNAME        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE ARCV8020-GUSERNAME
             TO ARCD0103-GUSERNAME

           EXEC SQL
                 SELECT
                       GUSERNAME
                     , CNOME
                     , CFUNCAO
                     , CPERFIL
                     , CLINGUA
                     , GPASSWORD
                     , ISTATUS
                     , CEMPRESA
                     , CCENTRO
                     , CMOED
                     , MCUSTMED
                     , DDATINI
                     , DDATFIM
                     , CUSERID
                     , HTIMEST
                     , GEMAIL
                     , CTIPOUTIL
                 INTO
                       :ARCD0103-GUSERNAME
                     , :ARCD0103-CNOME
                     , :ARCD0103-CFUNCAO
                     , :ARCD0103-CPERFIL
                     , :ARCD0103-CLINGUA
                     , :ARCD0103-GPASSWORD
                     , :ARCD0103-ISTATUS
                     , :ARCD0103-CEMPRESA
                     , :ARCD0103-CCENTRO
                     , :ARCD0103-CMOED
                     , :ARCD0103-MCUSTMED
                     , :ARCD0103-DDATINI
                     , :ARCD0103-DDATFIM
                     , :ARCD0103-CUSERID
                     , :ARCD0103-HTIMEST
                     , :ARCD0103-GEMAIL
                     , :ARCD0103-CTIPOUTIL
                 FROM ARVT0103
                 WHERE
                   UPPER(GUSERNAME) = UPPER(:ARCD0103-GUSERNAME)
           END-EXEC


           MOVE CON-ARVT0100
             TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-OBTEM-DADOS - DEPOI' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'ARCD0103-GUSERNAME '      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
              MOVE  ARCD0103-GUSERNAME        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              MOVE 'SQLWARN0                ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(3)
              MOVE  SQLWARN0                  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)

              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 IF VIAL0001-CRIACAO
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO ARCV8021-GUSERNAME-S
                    MOVE ARCK0001-GUSERNAME-EXISTS
                      TO ARCV8021-GUSERNAME-MSG
                 ELSE
                    MOVE ARCD0103-GUSERNAME
                      TO ARCV8021-GUSERNAME
                    MOVE ARCD0103-CNOME
                      TO ARCV8021-CNOME
                    MOVE ARCD0103-CFUNCAO
                      TO ARCV8021-CFUNCAO
                    MOVE ARCD0103-CTIPOUTIL
                      TO ARCV8021-CTIPOUTIL
                    MOVE ARCD0103-CPERFIL
                      TO ARCV8021-CPERFIL
                    MOVE ARCD0103-CLINGUA
                      TO ARCV8021-CLINGUA
      *             MOVE VIAL0001-IDIOMA
      *               TO ARCV8021-CLINGUA
                    MOVE ARCD0103-CEMPRESA
                      TO ARCV8021-CEMPRESA
                    MOVE ARCD0103-GEMAIL
                      TO ARCV8021-GEMAIL
                    MOVE ARCD0103-ISTATUS
                      TO ARCV8021-ISTATUS
                    MOVE ARCD0103-DDATINI
                      TO ARCV8021-DDATINI
                    MOVE ARCD0103-DDATFIM
                      TO ARCV8021-DDATFIM
                 END-IF
              ELSE
                 IF NOT VIAL0001-CRIACAO
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO ARCV8021-GUSERNAME-S
                    MOVE ARCK0001-GUSERNAME-N-EXISTS
                      TO ARCV8021-GUSERNAME-MSG
                 ELSE
                    PERFORM 2150-VALIDA-ESTRUTURA
                       THRU 2150-VALIDA-ESTRUTURA-EXIT
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2199-OBTEM-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *                       2150-VALIDA-ESTRUTURA
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       2150-VALIDA-ESTRUTURA.
      *
           IF ETCL0002-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2150-VALIDA-ESTRUTURA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           PERFORM VARYING WS-APLIC-LENGTH FROM 1 BY 1
             UNTIL ARCV8020-GUSERNAME(WS-APLIC-LENGTH:1) = SPACES
                OR WS-APLIC-LENGTH = 20
                   CONTINUE
           END-PERFORM.
      *
           IF ARCV8020-GUSERNAME(WS-APLIC-LENGTH:) NOT EQUAL SPACES
           AND WS-APLIC-LENGTH NOT EQUAL 20
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                                           TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                                           TO ARCV8021-GUSERNAME-S
              MOVE ARCK0001-GUSERNAME-A-EXISTS
                                           TO ARCV8021-GUSERNAME-MSG
           END-IF.
      *
       2150-VALIDA-ESTRUTURA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *                       2200-CALC-OTP
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       2200-CALC-OTP.
      *
           IF ETCL0002-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2300-CALC-OTP        ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM VIACP001-OBTEM-TOKEN
              THRU VIACP001-OBTEM-TOKEN-EXIT.

           MOVE VIACW001-TOKEN          TO ARCV8020-NOTP
                                           ARCV8021-NOTP
      *
       2200-CALC-OTP-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF ETCL0002-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA  ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'ARCV8020-NOTP        ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  ARCV8020-NOTP          TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'ARCV8021-NOTP        ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
              MOVE  ARCV8021-NOTP          TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE ARCV8021-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE ARCV8021-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE ARCV8021-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIACP001 END-EXEC.
           COPY VIAP0015.
           COPY VIAP0016.
           COPY ARCR2206.
      *==============================================================
